					<p class="paragrafoPost">
						There are many business plans on the market today for companies 
						that help them to have a North, especially at the beginning, 
						and to make a constant observation of their health. These plans 
						always have three bases: financial, organizational and efficiency. 
						This work, although difficult, is essential for the company 
						to bear fruits in the future.
					</p>
					
					<p class="paragrafoPost">
						In order to measure the desired reach of our company in the market 
						and the focus that we must have, we can use 
						the Business Model Canvas, for example. In this business plan 
						the manager evaluates points such as the target customer, 
						how to get them, how to keep our company productive, and 
						what cash flow we should get in and out. BMC is a great 
						tool to validate your business, evaluate whether the 
						company has good chances in the market, or not, among 
						other features. However, you should always consider one 
						or more plans to validate your company, not forgetting 
						that this evaluation has to be periodic and that 
						Business Model Canvas is not the only means, and 
						not necessarily the best to your business.
					</p>
					
					<p class="paragrafoPost">
						Finally, having done this, one must organize 
						the company so that there is no wastage, rework 
						or serious organizational error. One of the ways 
						to achieve efficiency in administration is by using 
						business management softwares that fits the needs of 
						your company. In the market, there are several solutions 
						that can be focused on a certain area or process and also 
						the solutions that integrate all the sectors of your business. 
						But then, after all this investment and study, 
						can we ensure that your company will succeed in 
						the market? No, but you're much more likely to thrive.
					</p>
					
